title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Asked about social need, Burdette said, 'Our safety net has a lot of holes in it.”' [From the Parkersburg (West Virginia) News, 30 October 1986. submitted by Glade Little, Parkersburg.]
